title: Tactical Tips: Positioning in Combat – Warhammer 40,000
description: Get the most out of close combat in the new edition of Warhammer 40,000 with these top tips.

title: How to Paint: Battle Ready Ultramarines Lieutenant with Combi-weapon
description:
Clad in Phobos armour and salvaged Tyranid chitin, this Lieutenant infiltrates enemy lines as an assassin and intelligencer. Follow this step-by-step guide to get your Lieutenant with Combi-weapon ready to collect tactical data on the gaming table in no time.

If you're new to painting - check out our Citadel Colour Painting Essentials videos to learn all about it

title: How to Paint: Battle Ready Tyranid Von Ryan's Leapers
description:
Von Ryan's Leapers reveal themselves in a blur of bladed limbs, eviscerating their unsuspecting prey in seconds. In this guide we'll be showing you how to paint a Von Ryan's Leaper to Battle Ready, then a few extra steps to take them to the next level.        

If you're new to painting - check out our Citadel Colour Painting Essentials videos to learn all about it.
